# Dependency Management

Best practices for managing external dependencies in the extension.

<rule>
name: dependency_management
description: Recommends using well-maintained libraries, regular updates, and minimizing external dependencies.

# Actual guidelines:
- Prefer well-maintained and reputable libraries.
- Regularly review and update dependencies, paying attention to breaking changes.
- Strive to minimize the number of external dependencies to reduce extension size and potential conflicts.
</rule>
